{"tid":2464200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB 班賤種唔係第一次咁搞人 之前試過屈街外人非禮","createTime":"2021-03-27T09:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T09:43:28.000Z","uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"27b4cff534039d1642cc93c9e22632d6d1c1b3d5","tid":2464200,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇印象 早5-6年前香港YouTuber開始做起個陣集體都係諷刺返無線做大台<br />\nCCTVB 條氣唔鋸就搞過一個叫 <span class=\"red\">網絡挑機</span> 既節目 <br />\n但其實只係以佢地剪接既技巧黎玩抹黑返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>無綫編導岑應繼《盛女愛作戰》及《沒女大翻身》後，近日邀請近20位網絡紅人拍攝新一輯真人騷《網絡挑機》，包括司徒夾帶、JFung、伍公子、大埔Lulu和Eminleo等，聲稱讓一班Youtuber進行各式各樣惡搞二次創作，任由大家插爆無綫劇集和綜藝節目等，欲借助新媒體力谷傳統媒體收視，節目還請來劉以達扮方丈自抽。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">節目昨晚首播前夕，有份演出的Youtuber伍公子於昨日凌晨在facebook狂插遭無綫河蟹，呼籲大家熄機勿捧場。伍公子留言謂：「記得一開波，我就問監製：『你個節目到底想點？』監製話：『我要個節目爆。』到開鏡時，我XX阿姐唱歌好X難聽，後來聽講啲focus group睇到都話大快人心，不過TVB就話我太X街，成段剪走晒。結論係，X街又嫌太X街，X又嫌太X，乜都剪走晒，我真係唔知個節目點爆，可能《愛．回家》仲好睇。」氣得編導岑應在fb爆粗還拖說：「唔玩得就咪X學人嚟玩。」火藥味十足。</span></span>但有網民就認為一班Youtuber過往經常寸爆無綫，為對方拍攝節目實在不智，如今又呼籲罷睇，實在「又要威又要戴頭盔」，甚至質疑Youtuber與無綫夾計力谷收視。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20151201/7FQGQKSFZEYM6QZIXITY26KPZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20151201%2F7FQGQKSFZEYM6QZIXITY26KPZQ%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr38wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=d213db56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20151201%2F7FQGQKSFZEYM6QZIXITY26KPZQ%2F&h=4aec1696\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20151201/7FQGQKSFZEYM6QZIXITY26KPZQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係其中一集內容 大概就係搵條女叫kibi 兩個睇下件泳衣點<br />\n然後一野撲落薑檸樂度再大叫非禮 <br />\n跟住門口成班仆街就衝入黎<br />\n類似傳統捉黃腳雞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">今次班賤種出黎認低威係因為知變左關公先出黎認衰仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma7ajzy4KPcoKCo1qRHtKCqXv8jxagznTDmTZiEKAkA4N?filename=3CzK81w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CzK81w.png&h=203c5926&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ9jQ8qxBsNMeVLCpxzjHd7ADnPjkee9C5Ygj66NVMdMG?filename=OGmBfGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGmBfGx.png&h=de963526&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTp5mhsW2WdwcJABFDDqvRRgAFppuUgR6jjyGVB7DJHjB?filename=drwaj8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdrwaj8d.png&h=a1ff0c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNVbLGLovei6WfJsqbviigyU7eUehof8uFvRmkMhGtvtS?filename=z2qN6Oe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2qN6Oe.png&h=b042e278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW4Dpw3zQh7o6apySvPqzT4mbDUD4rDJnWNd34ZWtBMCT?filename=YY1Nnmz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY1Nnmz.png&h=7b412268&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWZdAGrNPMsHHQbbWjVtoEeGVHKgJ3ztEXoMXaRRCFMoU?filename=kN7481A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkN7481A.png&h=f3f6a622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60cafcfde09c8b10fcab1b388004ebb66a3d3f43","tid":2464200,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"明知又要參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73430a8955253c9e897997049c32eb6d09f84f1b","tid":2464200,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d2e1c71d250e3b42d531a186babeacd436dd09","tid":2464200,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60cafcfde09c8b10fcab1b388004ebb66a3d3f43","tid":2464200,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB